query:
SELECT 
  s.id as site_id,
  s.siteNumber,
  sc.name as centre_name,
  uc.name as category_name
FROM sites s
JOIN shopping_centres sc ON s.centreId = sc.id
LEFT JOIN site_usage_categories suc ON s.id = suc.siteId
LEFT JOIN usage_categories uc ON suc.categoryId = uc.id
WHERE sc.name LIKE '%Highlands%' AND s.siteNumber = '3' AND uc.name LIKE '%Book%';
